<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>'Tis but a Flesh Wound — Isaac Lindell</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,700;1,300;1,400;1,600&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   DESIGN TOKENS
───────────────────────────────────────── */
:root {
  --white:       #ffffff;
  --off:         #f6f5f2;
  --surface:     #eeecea;
  --border:      #dddbd6;
  --border-soft: #e8e6e1;

  --blue-deep:   #2c5f72;
  --blue-mid:    #3d7d96;
  --blue-light:  #5a9db5;
  --blue-pale:   #c8dfe8;
  --blue-wash:   #eaf3f7;

  --mah-dark:    #4a1e0e;
  --mah-mid:     #7c3b1e;
  --mah-warm:    #a05030;
  --mah-light:   #c47850;
  --mah-pale:    #f0ddd0;

  --brass:       #b08040;
  --brass-pale:  #f0e4c8;

  --ink:         #1a1612;
  --ink-mid:     #3a3228;
  --muted:       #7a7060;
  --faint:       #b0a898;

  --font-display: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
  --font-ui:      'Jost', sans-serif;

  --ease:  0.22s ease;
  --ease-enter: 0.5s ease;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   RESET
───────────────────────────────────────── */
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { font-size: 16px; scroll-behavior: smooth; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
body { background: var(--white); color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--font-ui); font-weight: 300; overflow-x: hidden; }
a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
button { font-family: var(--font-ui); cursor: pointer; border: none; background: none; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   PROGRESS BAR
───────────────────────────────────────── */
.progress-bar { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; z-index: 999; background: transparent; pointer-events: none; }
.progress-fill { height: 2px; width: 0%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--mah-warm)); transition: width 0.08s linear; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   PAGE SWITCHER
───────────────────────────────────────── */
.bl-page { display: none; }
.bl-page.active { display: block; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   CONDENSED HEADER
   Row 1: date | title | links
   Row 2: nav tabs
───────────────────────────────────────── */
/* ── SITE HEADER — two compact rows ── */
.site-header {
  position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 300;
  background: var(--white);
  border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0 3.5rem;
  height: 42px;
  gap: 0;
}

/* Left — date · title as one banner line */
.header-left {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0;
  height: 100%;
  padding-right: 2rem;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.header-date {
  font-size: 0.54rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--faint); white-space: nowrap; padding-right: 1rem;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border-soft); margin-right: 1rem;
}
.header-name {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0em; line-height: 1;
  color: var(--ink); cursor: pointer;
  transition: color var(--ease); white-space: nowrap;
}
.header-name:hover { color: var(--blue-deep); }

/* Center — nav tabs */
.nav-tabs {
  display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
  gap: 0; height: 100%;
}
.nav-tab {
  font-size: 0.54rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--faint); padding: 0 1rem;
  height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  transition: color var(--ease), border-color var(--ease);
}
.nav-tab.active, .nav-tab:hover { color: var(--ink); }
.nav-tab.active { border-bottom-color: var(--blue-mid); }

/* Right — links */
.header-links {
  display: flex; gap: 1.4rem; justify-content: flex-end; align-items: center;
  height: 100%;
  border-left: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  padding-left: 2rem;
}
.header-link {
  font-size: 0.54rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; transition: color var(--ease);
  background: none; border: none; font-family: var(--font-ui); padding: 0;
}
.header-link:hover { color: var(--blue-deep); }

/* legacy .top-bar used in article/about pages — slim version */
.top-bar {
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  padding: 0.45rem 3.5rem;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  background: var(--white);
  position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 300;
}
.top-date { font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--faint); }
.top-links { display: flex; gap: 1.6rem; }
.top-link {
  font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; transition: color var(--ease);
  background: none; border: none; font-family: var(--font-ui); padding: 0;
}
.top-link:hover { color: var(--blue-deep); }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   SITE WRAP
───────────────────────────────────────── */
.wrap { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 3.5rem; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   HERO SECTION
───────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero-section {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 3fr 1px 2fr; gap: 0 2.5rem;
  padding: 2.8rem 0 2.8rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.55s 0.1s ease forwards;
}
.hero-divider { background: var(--border-soft); }

.hero-kicker {
  font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--mah-warm); margin-bottom: 1rem;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
}
.hero-kicker::after { content: ''; width: 20px; height: 1px; background: var(--mah-warm); }

.hero-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
  font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.0; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  cursor: pointer; transition: color var(--ease);
}
.hero-title:hover { color: var(--mah-mid); }

.hero-dek {
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.15rem; font-style: italic;
  line-height: 1.85; color: var(--ink-mid); margin-bottom: 1.4rem; max-width: 54ch;
}
.hero-byline {
  font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--faint); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
}
.byline-dot { width: 3px; height: 3px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--border); flex-shrink: 0; }

/* hero read button */
.hero-read {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem;
  font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--white); background: var(--blue-deep);
  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.6rem;
  transition: background var(--ease);
}
.hero-read:hover { background: var(--blue-mid); }

/* sidebar */
.sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding-left: 0.25rem; }
.side-item {
  padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer;
}
.side-item:last-child { border: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
.side-item:hover .side-title { color: var(--blue-mid); }
.side-kicker {
  font-size: 0.58rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--blue-mid); margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.side-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.28; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  transition: color var(--ease);
}
.side-dek {
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.92rem; font-style: italic;
  line-height: 1.7; color: var(--muted);
}
.side-meta { font-size: 0.62rem; color: var(--faint); margin-top: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   SECTION RULE
───────────────────────────────────────── */
.section-rule {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
  padding: 2.5rem 0 1.8rem;
}
.section-rule-label {
  font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink); white-space: nowrap;
}
.section-rule-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   FILTER BAR
───────────────────────────────────────── */
.filter-bar { display: flex; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft); }
.filter-tab {
  font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted); padding: 0.75rem 0; margin-right: 2rem;
  border-bottom: 1.5px solid transparent; margin-bottom: -1px;
  transition: color var(--ease), border-color var(--ease);
}
.filter-tab.active { color: var(--ink); border-bottom-color: var(--blue-mid); }
.filter-tab:hover:not(.active) { color: var(--ink-mid); }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   CARD GRID
───────────────────────────────────────── */
.cards-row {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  border-top: 2px solid var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 5rem;
}
.piece-card {
  padding: 1.5rem 1.6rem;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  cursor: pointer;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px);
  transition: opacity var(--ease-enter), transform var(--ease-enter), background var(--ease);
  position: relative;
}
.piece-card::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--blue-pale);
  transform: scaleX(0);
  transform-origin: left;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}
.piece-card:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }
.piece-card:last-child { border-right: none; }
.piece-card:hover { background: var(--blue-wash); }
.piece-card.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

.card-genre {
  font-size: 0.58rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
}
.genre-story  { color: var(--mah-warm); }
.genre-think  { color: var(--blue-mid); }
.genre-film   { color: var(--blue-mid); }
.genre-book   { color: var(--brass); }
.genre-poem   { color: var(--brass); }

.card-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.3; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  transition: color var(--ease);
}
.piece-card:hover .card-title { color: var(--blue-deep); }
.card-excerpt {
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.88rem; font-style: italic;
  line-height: 1.75; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.card-meta { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
.card-date { font-size: 0.62rem; color: var(--faint); letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
.card-arrow {
  font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--blue-pale);
  transition: color var(--ease), transform var(--ease);
}
.piece-card:hover .card-arrow { color: var(--blue-mid); transform: translateX(3px); }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   ARTICLE PAGE
───────────────────────────────────────── */
.article-outer { background: var(--white); min-height: 100vh; }
.article-wrap  { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 2rem 6rem; }

.article-back {
  font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  transition: color var(--ease), gap var(--ease);
}
.article-back:hover { color: var(--blue-deep); gap: 0.85rem; }

.article-genre {
  font-size: 0.58rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
  display: block; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}
.article-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
  font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}
.article-dateline {
  font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--faint); padding-bottom: 2rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft); margin-bottom: 2.8rem;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem;
}
.dateline-dot { width: 3px; height: 3px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--border); }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   PROSE
───────────────────────────────────────── */
.prose {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.92;
  color: var(--ink-mid); max-width: 65ch;
}
.prose p { margin-bottom: 1.6em; }
.prose p:first-of-type::first-letter {
  font-size: 4.5rem; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal;
  float: left; line-height: 0.8; margin: 0.08em 0.1em 0 0;
  color: var(--mah-mid);
}
.prose h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--ink); margin: 2.5em 0 0.7em; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.prose h3 {
  font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted); margin: 2.5em 0 1em;
}
.prose blockquote {
  border-left: 2px solid var(--blue-mid);
  padding: 0.25rem 0 0.25rem 1.4rem;
  font-style: italic; color: var(--muted);
  margin: 2.2em 0; font-size: 1.12rem; line-height: 1.88;
}
.prose ul { margin: 1em 0 1.6em 1.2em; }
.prose li { margin-bottom: 0.7em; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; }
.prose strong { font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }
.prose em { font-style: italic; }
.prose a { color: var(--blue-mid); text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: var(--blue-pale); transition: text-decoration-color var(--ease); }
.prose a:hover { text-decoration-color: var(--blue-mid); }
.prose hr { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft); margin: 3rem 0; }
.datestamp {
  font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--mah-warm); margin: 2.2em 0 0.7em;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem;
}
.datestamp::after { content: ''; flex: 0 0 20px; height: 1px; background: var(--mah-warm); }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   ABOUT PAGE
───────────────────────────────────────── */
.about-outer { background: var(--white); min-height: 100vh; }
.about-wrap { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 2rem 6rem; }
.about-eyebrow {
  font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--mah-warm); margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}
.about-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
  font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 2rem;
  padding-bottom: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.015em;
}
.about-body {
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.18rem;
  line-height: 1.9; color: var(--ink-mid);
}
.about-body p { margin-bottom: 1.4em; }
.about-body a { color: var(--blue-mid); text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: var(--blue-pale); }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   FOOTER
───────────────────────────────────────── */
footer {
  background: var(--blue-deep);
  padding: 2.8rem 3.5rem;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem; align-items: center;
  position: relative;
}
footer::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--mah-mid), var(--blue-light), var(--brass), var(--blue-mid));
}
.footer-name {
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 400;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
}
.footer-sub {
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.88rem; font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(200,223,232,0.4); margin-top: 0.3rem;
}
.footer-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
.footer-links a, .footer-links button {
  font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(200,223,232,0.38); font-family: var(--font-ui); font-weight: 300;
  transition: color var(--ease); padding: 0;
}
.footer-links a:hover, .footer-links button:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88); }
.footer-right { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem; }
.footer-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--blue-pale); }
.footer-rule { width: 36px; height: 2px; background: var(--mah-light); }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   ANIMATIONS + UTILS
───────────────────────────────────────── */
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
}
.reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); transition: opacity var(--ease-enter), transform var(--ease-enter); }
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after { animation-duration: 0.01ms !important; transition-duration: 0.01ms !important; }
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────
   RESPONSIVE
───────────────────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .cards-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .piece-card:nth-child(2n) { border-right: none; }
  .hero-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem 0; }
  .hero-divider { display: none; }
  .wrap { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .site-header { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .header-links { gap: 1rem; }
  .top-bar, footer { padding-left: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1.5rem; }
  footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .footer-right { justify-content: flex-start; }
}
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .site-header { grid-template-columns: 1fr; height: auto; padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; gap: 0.3rem; }
  .header-left { border-right: none; padding-right: 0; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .header-date { border-right: none; padding-right: 0; margin-right: 0; }
  .header-links { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; justify-content: flex-start; }
  .nav-tabs { justify-content: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cards-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .piece-card { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft); }
  .article-wrap, .about-wrap { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 5rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress"></div></div>

<!-- ══ HOME ══ -->
<div id="page-home" class="bl-page active">

  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="header-left">
      <span class="header-date">Nashville, TN &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span id="today-date"></span></span>
      <span class="header-name" onclick="showHome()">'Tis but a Flesh Wound</span>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-tabs">
      <button class="nav-tab active" onclick="filterSection('all',this)">All</button>
      <button class="nav-tab" onclick="filterSection('story',this)">Stories</button>
      <button class="nav-tab" onclick="filterSection('think-piece',this)">Think Pieces</button>
      <button class="nav-tab" onclick="filterSection('film-review',this)">Film Reviews</button>
      <button class="nav-tab" onclick="showAbout()">About</button>
    </div>
    <div class="header-links">
      <a class="header-link" href="https://letterboxd.com/isaaclindell/" target="_blank">Letterboxd</a>
      <a class="header-link" href="https://lindellsblog.blogspot.com" target="_blank">Archive</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="wrap">

    <div class="hero-section" id="hero-section">
      <div>
        <div class="hero-kicker" id="hero-kicker">Featured Story</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title" id="hero-title" onclick="">Dirt</h1>
        <p class="hero-dek" id="hero-dek">The butterflies in Paisley's stomach were not from nervous excitement. These were yellowjackets — sharp pangs of terror as she drove the dusty soil on Oil Springs Road into the Wyoming desert, 1958.</p>
        <div class="hero-byline">
          Isaac Lindell
          <span class="byline-dot"></span>
          <span id="hero-date">November 16, 2025</span>
          <span class="byline-dot"></span>
          <span id="hero-mins">25 min read</span>
        </div>
        <button class="hero-read" id="hero-read">Read Story →</button>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-divider"></div>
      <div class="sidebar" id="sidebar"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-rule reveal">
      <div class="section-rule-label">More Writing</div>
      <div class="section-rule-line"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="filter-bar reveal">
      <button class="filter-tab active" onclick="filterGrid('all',this)" id="ftab-all">All</button>
      <button class="filter-tab" onclick="filterGrid('story',this)" id="ftab-story">Stories</button>
      <button class="filter-tab" onclick="filterGrid('think-piece',this)" id="ftab-think">Think Pieces</button>
      <button class="filter-tab" onclick="filterGrid('film-review',this)" id="ftab-film">Film Reviews</button>
    </div>

    <div class="cards-row" id="cards-row"></div>

  </div>

  <footer class="reveal">
